Insurance Policy Claims Component

This component is composed of a FlexCard and the LWC compiled from the FlexCard: 
FlexCard: insPolicyClaimsContainer_nds
LWC: cfInsPolicyClaimsContainer_nds
Label: Insurance Policy Claims Container Newport

The parts of this component are:
Text label: Open Claims
Open claims displayed in a child component.

You can click the name of the claim to go to the claim detail page.
FlexCard Structure
This FlexCard has a text element that displays the label we chose and holds the insPolicyClaimsChild_nds child FlexCard.

Customize this Component
To learn about how to customize this kind of component, see the Digital Experience Site Component Customization Overview

Insurance Policy Claims Child Component
Use the Insurance Policy Claims Child component to show your Policyholder site users a snapshot of their open claims on a policy and link them to additional information about the claim.
